Chelsea Noble (born Nancy Mueller, December 4, 1964) is a former American actress. She is known for her role as Kate MacDonald on the television sitcom Growing Pains (1989–1992). She is the wife of her former Growing Pains co-star, Kirk Cameron, and the sister-in-law of former Full House star Candace Cameron Bure.
